        "content": "<p>Currently, the console doesn't show stack trace. Because it handles panic by itself, LLDB doesn't show stack trace either (without breakpoint).</p>\n<p>code:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">IO</span> <span class=\"n\">Unit</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">panic</span><span class=\"bp\">!</span> <span class=\"s2\">\"Hello\"</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pure</span> <span class=\"o\">()</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">main</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">IO</span> <span class=\"n\">Unit</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">IO.println</span> <span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"bp\">!</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Hello, world!\"</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">foo</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>console:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Hello</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">world</span><span class=\"bp\">!</span>\n<span class=\"n\">PANIC</span> <span class=\"n\">at</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"n\">Main</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">4</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Hello</span>\n<span class=\"n\">backtrace</span><span class=\"o\">:</span>\n<span class=\"n\">build</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">panic</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">tb</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">0x29d2de</span><span class=\"o\">)[</span><span class=\"mi\">0x559cafc072de</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"n\">build</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">panic</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">tb</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">0xa46eb</span><span class=\"o\">)[</span><span class=\"mi\">0x559cafa0e6eb</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"n\">build</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">panic</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">tb</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">0xa4c67</span><span class=\"o\">)[</span><span class=\"mi\">0x559cafa0ec67</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lib</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">libc.so.6</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">0x23290</span><span class=\"o\">)[</span><span class=\"mi\">0x7f625afeb290</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lib</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">libc.so.6</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">__libc_start_main</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">0x8a</span><span class=\"o\">)[</span><span class=\"mi\">0x7f625afeb34a</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"n\">build</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span><span class=\"bp\">/</span><span class=\"n\">panic</span><span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">tb</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">0xa45e5</span><span class=\"o\">)[</span><span class=\"mi\">0x559cafa0e5e5</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"n\">uncaught</span> <span class=\"n\">exception</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">already</span> <span class=\"n\">exists</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">error</span> <span class=\"n\">code</span><span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Debug symbols are present with <code>objdump --sym build/bin/main</code>. There aren't in the backtrace.</p>",
